race.comment: TWILIGHT TALE (6) is worth following up. Beaten a head two back then was not far away last time in a richer race. Well weighted with the claim here but perhaps more importantly drawn much better than last time. Can bounce back. WEMBANYAMA (7) got back but ran on hard to score last time with Pike in the saddle. Peak fitness and now back in form can go close again. I'M NIPOTE (9) has placed at both runs this time in and looks close to a win. Goes well third-up and should feature again. MORE THAN ENUFF (8) has been thereabouts without winning. Best figures stack up but will need a little luck off the wide draw here. I'M CRAFTY (5) was a fresh-up winner then bombed the start and solid in a tough race last time. Worth another chance and could be overs here.
